*.7z

# ============================================================================
# IMPORTANT REMINDERS
# ============================================================================
# 
# ✅ Always review files before committing:
#    git status
#    git diff
#
# ✅ Never commit:
#    - AWS credentials or access keys
#    - Terraform state files
#    - .tfvars files with sensitive data
#    - Private keys or certificates
#
# ✅ Use git-secrets or similar tools to prevent credential leaks:
#    https://github.com/awslabs/git-secrets
#
# ============================================================================

# Project-specific ignores
terraform/terraform.tfvars

# Note: .terraform.lock.hcl SHOULD be committed for version consistency
# It's already covered by the general pattern above, but explicitly NOT ignored here
